# Histograms for different set types in Squash App

### Who

<!--Who does this benefit or who will this affect? Who should be able to view this?-->

- Players with an account

### What

<!--What problem needs addressing?-->

- Once we have a login system implemented, a user should be able to go to their own user page and see some basic information about all the games they've played
- This overview should be basic and can also bring them to the specific apps

### Why

<!--What value does this add?-->

- A user who has played multiple games should be able to see their stats on these games quickly at a glance, without having to navigate to each app individually

### Acceptance Criteria

<!--Testable done conditions; avoid implementation detail.-->

- [ ] A user can view their own profile
- [ ] (Optional) Each user has a public profile with some basic info, like [here](https://www.lichess4545.com/team4545/season/48/player/MilsBees/)
